title: Garangsewi thangkisewi
lyrics:
Garangsewi thangkisewi
Rwjab Halleluiya Hossanna -2
Subungni raja, Buhumni raja
Rongza boibw rongza -2
(A)
Honwi naihor Menda bisaya
Gadha bisayao daogabwgou
Somaihwdwng subung hanzaya
Bifang bilaijwng somaihwdwng -2
Subungni raja, Buhumni raja
Rongza boibw rongza -2
